    <title>New release for Zitadel: v2.52.0</title>
    <updated>2024-05-16T01:38:37-04:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>zitadel/zitadel</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;h1&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/compare/v2.51.4...v2.52.0"&gt;2.52.0&lt;/a&gt; (2024-05-16)&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Bug Fixes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;allow other users to set up MFAs (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/7914"&gt;#7914&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/5bf195d37479090577b635cbb980cf9ec43621dc"&gt;5bf195d&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;allow start and retrieve IdP intents with IdPs from other organizations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/7871"&gt;#7871&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/72c5b057f1370724af07a097b6ac78cfcfe590c5"&gt;72c5b05&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;console:&lt;/strong&gt; password reset hidden texts (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/7915"&gt;#7915&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/016e5e5da1680f776aac07576969157658513dd5"&gt;016e5e5&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;defaults:&lt;/strong&gt; configure hashers via env (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/7872"&gt;#7872&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/24a9d7c730f1095590642fa3d9c7c8b6b3828d6e"&gt;24a9d7c&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;login:&lt;/strong&gt; check for error before automatic idp redirect (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/7891"&gt;#7891&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/d177b82d2d341bca8efb18b728d71743d9e3f827"&gt;d177b82&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;smtp:&lt;/strong&gt; enable default instance config (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/7925"&gt;#7925&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/f3abbad1330f3c689c3d510a701e1573117ef682"&gt;f3abbad&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Features&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;add action v2 execution on requests and responses (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/7637"&gt;#7637&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/1c5ecba42a8ffb5b366db9c5ca28a7170cdd33a1"&gt;1c5ecba&lt;/a&gt;), closes &lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/7735"&gt;#7735&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/releases/tag/v2.52.0" rel="alternate"/>
